snippet.textDisplay: you wanna know something funny, I've been watching his youtube vlogs for a long time, like when he was going to gabbie's apartment and scaring Alex in the hallway of their apartment, but I always joke around about how nice it would be if David surprised me, but im okay now. Im just so happy to know that there's still genuine people out there who actually strive to help others. I'm mormon and im going on a mission soon I have no idea where or when yet, but I receive my call this coming week while I'm in the Dominican Republic for two weeks. The point is as corny as it sounds I wanna love, and care, and help like David does, maybe being as funny as he is would help a little, but the heart, his heart, that's something that can't be taught, its genuinely him and I hope I don't meet him now, but I hope that I meet him one day when I can say you made the world a better place just by being yourself, and here I am doing that too, just broke. much love David
